<p style=" font-family: Times; font-size: 11pt;">Congratulations! Your application for the <Strong>Affirm Financial Services Consumer Loan has been approved</Strong> for a total loan amount of ${Full Loan Amount}.</p>
<p style=" font-family: Times; font-size: 11pt;">The term of the Loan is {Term} months, at an annual fixed interest rate of {APR} %. Each monthly payment is in the amount of ${Reg Pmt Amt} except for your first payment which will be in the amount of ${First Pmt Amt} and is payable on day {Pay Day} of each month starting {First Payment Date}. You also have the option of paying the balance due at any time with no additional fees.</p>
<p style=" font-family: Times; font-size: 11pt;">A copy of the Loan Agreement is enclosed for your review and signature as well as a Pre-Authorized Payment Form and a Disclosure Statement pertaining to the terms of your loan. Also included is a copy of your Disclosure Statement and our Privacy Policy for your review and your file. Please make sure you read them carefully.</p>
<p style=" font-family: Times; font-size: 11pt;">Please sign the appropriate documents and return original copies to the following address:</p>
