Station B, P.O. Box 53<br/> London, Ontario, N6A 4V3</p>
<p style=" font-family: Times; font-size: 11pt;">Keep in mind, one of the most important things to consider when it comes to your credit, is to make your full monthly payment on time as this weighs on your credit score.</p>
<p style=" font-family: Times; font-size: 11pt;">We thank you for your interest in working with Affirm Financial Services and we look forward to a long and mutually beneficial relationship.</p>
<p style=" font-family: Times; font-size: 11pt;">For any additional information regarding the terms of your loan, please do not hesitate to contact us at 1-855-220-7531.</p>
